title: Bunkercast XXV: Kyle Brandt Redemption
itunes:title: Bunkercast XXV: Kyle Brandt Redemption
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler are joined by Kyle Brandt to discuss all things football. The draft is quickly approaching, Dak Prescott had a party, and the first NFL player was diagnosed with Covid-19. Kyle brings back a segment that bombed so hard on GMFB involving Wess... is redemption in store?
